  "description": "Minimum aggression, maximum spatial expanse \u2014 the horizontal vastness of the deep-sea floor. Triangle src1 (smooth harmonics) with srcMix=0.0 (pure src1, undiluted). proc1=LP (560 Hz) with zero resonance and zero feedback \u2014 no drama, only filtering. Full spatial chain: fx1=Delay (long, 0.72 param), fx2=Reverb (0.72 mix, cavernous), fx3=Chorus (subtle width). Four mods at low depth: LFO->Pan (slow stereo survey, 0.01 Hz), Env->FilterCutoff (gentle), Velocity->Volume, Aftertouch->FXMix. aggression=0.05 is the floor. This is the sound of enormous horizontal distance, not depth.",
